text.tspan: Machine 0x14c architecture to run on (Arm, intel...)(i386)
NumberOfSections 3 number of entries in sections table
SizeOfOptionalHeader 0xe0 relative offset to the section table
Characteristics 0x102 is it an EXE, a DLL, ...(32b Executable)
ImageBase 0x400000 address it will be mapped in memory
SectionAlignment 0x1000 where sections should start in memory
FileAlignment 0x200 where sections should start on file
MajorSubsystemVersion 4 which Windows can run it ?
SizeOfImage 0x4000 total size of content to load
Subsystem 2 (GUI) is it a driver, a GUI binary,... ?
NumberOfRvaAndSizes 16 how many data directories ? (imports is #2)
defines how the file is loaded in memory
pointers to extra structures, such as exports, imports,...
(optional for non-standard PEs, but required for executables)
trampoline between the executable and Windows
